PQ%2F&h=beec605b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210202/M2FTGHWLVJDHHMEEQC5NO7AWPQ/</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T08:13:27.000Z","msg":"老師：小明，因咩你既作文，「我家的狗」同你哥哥舊年交個篇完全一樣？<br />\n小明：因為係同一隻狗嘛"},{"pid":"a39a49bc80e47f662dc1926e78ac1063075af8c4","tid":2391357,"uid":325580,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T08:13:33.000Z","msg":"?!;:&ldquo;&rdquo;［］「」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8d3a6436f7ab37005f1aa117edf79d8c789021f","tid":2391357,"uid":321194,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T08:15:21.000Z","msg":"，。？！、&hellip;&hellip;：；（）「」《》"},{"pid":"208c020388cb757d6a002f20a87ae3e368b31478","tid":2391357,"uid":387468,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4015e9391a12c394f6c02c23fbce7e74efa5e71d","tid":2391357,"uid":86509,"like":78,"dislike":0,"score":78,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T07:18:07.000Z","msg":"即係冇答過<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n是但啦法治已死"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T08:15:35.000Z","msg":"係啦<br />\n講一句法治已死幾輕鬆幾簡單幾抽離呀<br />\n手足坐監無計啦 政治監嘛 無法治啦嘛 預咗架啦<br />\n<br />\n咁撚冷血都講得出<br />\n屌你老母"},{"pid":"4a7e41bdc8876d39909a6fa4c3e3680d8e427766","tid":2391357,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T08:15:52.000Z","msg":"連抄功課都唔識<br />\n都係既 大學大專都冇上過<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cdc87aa64d1aac560813be501066fefd38b4233","tid":2391357,"uid":34777,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0d2090a6f510c50f669b12080921f065b2a588a4","tid":2391357,"uid":256246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T08:05:53.000Z","msg":"希望法庭受佢理變案例，咁第時就會無晒plagisarism, 仲可以寸返d professor轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T08:16:23.000Z","msg":"真<br />\nI am happy變做I am delighted <br />\n又冇事<img s